{"word":"Γάδαρα","slug":"Γάδαρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n21384\" key=\"*ga/dara\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Γάδᾰρα</orth> [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Γᾰ], <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ων</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen></foreign>, a town in Palestine, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:2:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.2.29</biblScope> </bibl>:—<orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Γᾰδᾰρεύς</orth> or <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Γᾰδᾰρηνός</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, an inhabitant, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0031.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Ev.Matt.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.28</biblScope> </bibl>:—<orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Γᾰδᾰρίς</orth> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γῆ</foreign>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, the country, Str.l.c.</entryFree>"}]}